official_title: A bill to permit certain individuals who claim title to certain land in the Parish of Plaquemines, La., to bring an action against the United States to determine ownership of the land.

summary.text: Permits individuals who claim title to specified land in the parish of Plaquemines, Louisiana, to bring an action against the United States to determine ownership of the land.

titles.title: A bill to permit certain individuals who claim title to certain land in the Parish of Plaquemines, La., to bring an action against the United States to determine ownership of the land.
